       *       operators that check emptiness without reading any elements). Now an {@link Iterator} counts as
       *       empty exactly if it has no elements left. (Note that this bug has never affected basic functionality, like
       *       {@code <#list ...>}.) 
       *     </li>  
       *     <li>
       *       <p>2.3.26 (or higher):
